message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with medical image segmentation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV) and medical imaging (cs.MED). The paper also proposes a novel learning method using forward-backward consistency, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks for segmentation, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NEURON).
